Name: Victor Pachas
Description:
Victor was beaten, stabbed, slashed, and asphyxiated by Carlos Camacho after he discovered that they were transgender.

> Camacho beat, stabbed, slashed, and asphyxiated Pachas by stepping on [their] throat. The killing was so brutal that the Genessee Avenue apartment was splattered with blood and police could not tell initially how Pachas died. Camacho's lawyer argued that his client became so enraged after learning he had picked up a transvestite, he reacted with fear and revulsion.
